a selfish child...!

31
00:02:49,875 --> 00:02:53,509
You only escaped with your
life because you were lucky!

32
00:02:54,375 --> 00:02:55,642
You don't have to
do everything all

33
00:02:55,642 --> 00:02:56,975
on your own, you know...

34
00:02:56,975 --> 00:02:59,309
You can lean on other people.

35
00:03:01,642 --> 00:03:03,242
Like us...

36
00:03:03,242 --> 00:03:06,275
